           move      w-red-prt-mag-acs    to   w-red-prt-mag-saa      .
           move      w-tes-cod-dpz        to   w-red-prt-mag-dpz      .
           move      w-red-prt-mag-acn    to   w-red-prt-mag-nnn      .
           move      w-red-prt-mag-prt    to   w-tes-num-prt          .
           if        w-red-prt-mag-nnn    =    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-tes-num-prt          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Find                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                not  = "FIND"
                     go to acc-num-prt-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Find su archivio [mmt]                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   fnd-arc-mmt-000      thru fnd-arc-mmt-999        .
           if        w-fnd-arc-mmt-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-num-prt-100.
