           if        w-red-prt-mag-dpz    =    w-tes-cod-dpz
                     go to acc-num-prt-220.
           move      spaces               to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           string    "Il movimento non e' della dipendenza "
                                delimited by   size
                     w-tes-cod-dpz
                                delimited by   size
                     ", ma della dipendenza "
                                delimited by   size
                     w-red-prt-mag-dpz
                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-err-box-err-msg      .
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
           go to     acc-num-prt-100.
       acc-num-prt-220.
