      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      08                   to   v-car                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      57                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Valore :"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
