      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se inserimento                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "I"
                     go to scr-mov-fil-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Write record [mmt]                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   wrt-rec-mmt-000      thru wrt-rec-mmt-999        .
